I<br>presume that all scholarship-funded fee components are generally shared<br>pro rata regardless of local regulations about fee collection. But what<br>arrangements are being made with respect to full fee paying students - do<br>you collect anything on behalf of these partners? We coordinate 2 and are a partner in the 3rd. Our partners are in Norway, Sweden, Spain, France and Hungary and we have associate partners in Botswana, India, Malaysia, the Lebanon and Serbia (among others).<br>I've worked on erasmus masters degrees for 5 years and have found them to be very rewarding but very hard work and those working on them can feel isolated.
